item.title: Hayley Williams Surprise-Releases 17 New Songs on Her Website
item.description: Paramore lead singer Hayley Williams has surprise-released 17 new songs on her website. Fans were given an access code as part of the new drop from Williams’ Good Dye Young hair dye company. Upo
